    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>Welcome to Food Inc: Home of the Supply</strong></i> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        <strong>A cooperative adventure</strong> that invites you to build and improve your own farm! Up to 4 players you can plant crops as the seasons change, construct buildings for your needs and heal your animals when needed. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199900/extras/5692557bc73a814c3342ce253a4888b6.poster.avif?t=1741854866\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199900/extras/5692557bc73a814c3342ce253a4888b6.webm?t=1741854866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199900/extras/5692557bc73a814c3342ce253a4888b6.mp4?t=1741854866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        <strong>Ride your horse</strong> and step into the shoes of a real farmer with an immersive third and first person view. Discover every part of food inc: Home of the Supply, a game that blends realistic elements with arcade ones.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199900/extras/4ad25dec9a52f191ecdbe7accd6ee3f3.poster.avif?t=1741854866\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199900/extras/4ad25dec9a52f191ecdbe7accd6ee3f3.webm?t=1741854866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199900/extras/4ad25dec9a52f191ecdbe7accd6ee3f3.mp4?t=1741854866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        <strong>Explore the villages</strong> from the desert while collecting recources and unlocking new things. Discover the hole desert with your pickup truck and enjoy the unknown.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199900/extras/da7d82a14c0af7ac0cc78f178fc21c01.poster.avif?t=1741854866\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199900/extras/da7d82a14c0af7ac0cc78f178fc21c01.webm?t=1741854866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199900/extras/da7d82a14c0af7ac0cc78f178fc21c01.mp4?t=1741854866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        <strong>Drive around</strong> to pick and deliver packages in order to improve your farming skills. Remember to feed your animals regularly so they can grow, and check on them frequently to heal any that may have gotten sick.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199900/extras/ec1d0be6dd31d6f1f9472d36b3301cb9.poster.avif?t=1741854866\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199900/extras/ec1d0be6dd31d6f1f9472d36b3301cb9.webm?t=1741854866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199900/extras/ec1d0be6dd31d6f1f9472d36b3301cb9.mp4?t=1741854866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>All you can do and much more to come</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        In food Inc: Home of the Supply, you can: construct buildings, plant crops and trees, gather resources, unlock new skills, complete missions, expand your farm by unlocking new zones, complete achievements, unlock skins for your farmer and horse, raise animals, discover new areas, go fishing and mining, care for bees, refine new items, ride your horse through the farm, drive your pickup through the desert, and do all of this with your friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
